title: 173: The Target Haul Episode (Summer '22 Edition)
itunes:title: The Target Haul Episode (Summer '22 Edition)
description: In this episode, Lisa and the crew taste-tested a dozen fun and unique finds from Target! Stuff like a plant-based Philly cheesesteak pocket, another great chicken dish from Kevin’s Natural Foods, a plant-based quesadilla from the Tattooed Chef, a brand-new boxed macaroni find, birthday cake granola, and SO MUCH MORE. Plus, a unique sweet-treat find from Dr. Praeger that’s packed with veggies! No time to wait: Push play now, then head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of the products mentioned in the episode.
itunes:summary: It’s time for a brand new Target Haul and boy, did we hit the bullseye on a few finds!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
dc:creator: Lisa Lillien
